[00:09.48]	As Phaethon would whip you to the west,
[00:13.10]	And bring in cloudy night immediately.
[00:16.64]	Spread thy close curtain, love-performing night,
[00:20.90]	That runaway's eyes may wink and Romeo
[00:24.51]	Leap to these arms, untalk'd of and unseen.
[00:28.37]	Lovers can see to do their amorous rites
